Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.06,0:16:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你经常接触噪音\N{\rEng}your exposure to noise
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,还是因为自身免疫\N{\rEng}or it's an autoimmune issue
