Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,对于听力严重受损或者\N{\rEng}For people with severe hearing loss or
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,完全失聪的人来说  确实有用\N{\rEng}complete deafness, yes, they help.
