Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.04,0:25:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Okay, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.24,0:25:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好  谢谢\N{\rEng}Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.93,0:25:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢  我真的很感激你\N{\rEng}Thank you so much. I really, really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.57,0:25:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.47,0:25:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我会告诉他\N{\rEng}No, yeah, I'll tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.67,0:25:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.49,0:25:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\N{\rEng}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.74,0:25:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,说了什么\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.17,0:25:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他找了个地方\N{\rEng}He's found a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.46,0:27:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord0\shad1}失聪儿童区
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.40,0:27:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是他吗\N{\rEng}Is that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.29,0:27:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁本\N{\rEng}Ruben.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.69,0:27:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  抱歉  我不会手语\N{\rEng}Hi. I don't... I'm sorry, I don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.10,0:27:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我是鲁本\N{\rEng}I'm Ruben.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.05,0:27:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这是露\N{\rEng}Yeah, this is Lou.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.46,0:27:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  我是露\N{\rEng}Hi. I'm... I'm Lou.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.87,0:28:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我要读唇语\N{\rEng}I'm sorry, I read lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.21,0:28:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫露\N{\rEng}M- My name is Lou.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.24,0:28:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-露  我是乔  -你好  乔\N{\rEng}- Lou. I'm Joe. - Hi, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.20,0:28:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-介意我跟他聊聊吗  -不介意\N{\rEng}- You mind if I borrow him for a minute? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.02,0:28:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我们聊的时候\N{\rEng}All right, you mind watching my beast here for me
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.87,0:28:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你能帮我看着狗吗\N{\rEng}while we have a talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.47,0:28:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Well, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.49,0:28:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,露  这是路易\N{\rEng}Lou, this is Louie.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.81,0:28:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,它是我的助听犬\N{\rEng}He's my hearing dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.01,0:28:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,它告诉我你们到了\N{\rEng}He let me know you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.28,0:28:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,它的名字取自59年白袜队球员\N{\rEng}I named it after Louie Aparicio
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.87,0:28:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-路易·阿帕里西奥  -好\N{\rEng}- from the White Sox in '59. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.75,0:28:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,要想跟它打好关系\N{\rEng}You want to be best friends with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.70,0:28:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-就给它吃这个  -好的\N{\rEng}- give him one of these. - Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.99,0:28:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-好吗  -好\N{\rEng}- Okay? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.12,0:28:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...\N{\rEng}Yo, what about...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.22,0:28:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,露  你来吗\N{\rEng}Lou, you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.18,0:28:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不  你去吧\N{\rEng}No, no, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.10,0:28:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-你确定吗  -确定\N{\rEng}- You sure? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.88,0:28:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不会花太久  好吗  -好\N{\rEng}- I won't be long, okay? - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.38,0:28:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,乖乖的\N{\rEng}You be a good boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.30,0:29:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.30,0:29:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,测试\N{\rEng}Test.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.49,0:29:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.83,0:29:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这个能用\N{\rEng}So, it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.20,0:29:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你看这个可以吗\N{\rEng}Is this okay for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.76,0:29:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可以  你能听见我说话吗\N{\rEng}Yeah, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.18,0:29:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不能  我读你的唇语\N{\rEng}No. No, I'm gonna read your lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.20,0:29:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会漏掉一些  但我尽量  好吗\N{\rEng}I might miss some things, but I'm gonna try, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.85,0:29:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-好  -你说话尽量吐字清晰\N{\rEng}- Okay. - Just try, try to speak clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.99,0:29:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.07,0:30:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗  鲁本\N{\rEng}How are you, Ruben?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.17,0:30:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord0\shad1}你好吗  鲁本
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.30,0:30:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我还好\N{\rEng}I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.73,0:30:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你有毒瘾吗\N{\rEng}You're an addict?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.91,0:30:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.33,0:30:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哪种毒品\N{\rEng}What sort of drugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.15,0:30:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我吸哪种毒品\N{\rEng}What'd I take?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.11,0:30:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,来者不拒\N{\rEng}Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.88,0:30:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,主要是海洛因\N{\rEng}Mainly heroin.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.61,0:30:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,海洛因\N{\rEng}Heroin.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.11,0:30:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你失去听力后  想过要吸毒吗\N{\rEng}Have you thought about using since you lost your hearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.94,0:30:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不太好过\N{\rEng}Today is not a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.94,0:31:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我头脑不清楚\N{\rEng}I'm not thinking clear today.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.30,0:31:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,聊聊我的情况吧\N{\rEng}Let's talk about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.41,0:31:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我酗酒\N{\rEng}I'm an alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.67,0:31:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,越战的时候  一枚炸弹在我身边爆炸\N{\rEng}I lost my hearing in the Vietnam War
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.50,0:31:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我因此失去了听力\N{\rEng}when a bomb exploded near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.82,0:31:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我还记得那枚炸弹爆炸时\N{\rEng}I still remember the music I was listening to
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.75,0:31:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我在听的音乐\N{\rEng}when that bomb went off.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.62,0:31:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之后  我失去了一切\N{\rEng}After that, I lost everything else -
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.71,0:31:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我的妻子  我的孩子\N{\rEng}my wife, my kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.89,0:31:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,注意  鲁本  那不是因为我聋了\N{\rEng}Not because of being deaf, mind you, Ruben.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.45,0:31:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,而是因为酗酒\N{\rEng}It was the beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.51,0:31:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你戒毒多久了\N{\rEng}How long you been clean?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.13,0:31:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,四年了\N{\rEng}Four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.35,0:31:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,四年\N{\rEng}Four?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.55,0:31:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在需要帮助吗\N{\rEng}And you need some help right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.68,0:31:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该去看看露\N{\rEng}Yo, I should check on Lou.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.49,0:31:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩在一起多久了\N{\rEng}How long you two been together?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.85,0:32:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,四年\N{\rEng}Four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.94,0:32:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你搞音乐  对吗\N{\rEng}You play music, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.11,0:32:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-不  -不\N{\rEng}- No. - No?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.25,0:32:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不搞了\N{\rEng}No, not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.66,0:32:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我得先去装植入设备\N{\rEng}Not until I get the implant.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.65,0:32:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-植入设备  -对\N{\rEng}- Implant? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.52,0:32:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  你了解现在的植入设备吗\N{\rEng}Sorry, you know about these implants they got now?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.67,0:32:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就是  他们有植入设备\N{\rEng}It's like... it's like, uh... th- they have implants.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.40,0:32:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  对\N{\rEng}I know. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.71,0:32:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很贵\N{\rEng}Expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.05,0:32:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,对  谢谢  确实很贵\N{\rEng}Yeah. Thank you. Yes, they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.01,0:32:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rEng}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.19,0:32:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你要明白\N{\rEng}You should understand that, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.10,0:32:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个失聪人士社区\N{\rEng}this is a Deaf community.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.11,0:32:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是有我的项目  我们属于\N{\rEng}Not just my program, but we're part
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.97,0:32:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord0\shad1}你要明白  鲁本\N这是个失聪人士社区  不只是有我的项目\N我们属于一个更大的失聪人士社区
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.01,0:32:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,一个更大的失聪人士社区\N{\rEng}of a larger Deaf community.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.50,0:33:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我的项目  和参加项目的人\N{\rEng}And my program, and the people in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.16,0:33:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,都从这个失聪人士社区中受益良多\N{\rEng}they benefit tremendously from that Deaf community.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.49,0:33:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们同他们合作\N{\rEng}We work with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.18,0:33:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他们也同我们合作\N{\rEng}and they work with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.15,0:33:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但有一点很重要\N{\rEng}But it's very important,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.42,0:33:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想留在这里\N{\rEng}if you want to be here,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.02,0:33:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你要明白  我们想要解决的\N{\rEng}to understand that we're looking for a solution to...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.64,0:33:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是思想的问题\N{\rEng}to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.26,0:33:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是听力的问题\N{\rEng}not this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.08,0:33:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫露也进来吧\N{\rEng}Why don't you go invite Lou in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.43,0:33:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.26,0:33:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,露\N{\rEng}Lou!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.04,0:33:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他想跟你谈谈\N{\rEng}This guy wants to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.30,0:33:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.36,0:33:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你现在应该\N{\rEng}Well... I think it's important
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.51,0:33:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,留在我们这里  鲁本\N{\rEng}that you stay here with us right now, Ruben,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.77,0:33:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,学点手语\N{\rEng}learn some sign language,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.67,0:33:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,踏踏实实地适应\N{\rEng}find some solid ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.66,0:34:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么想\N{\rEng}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.88,0:34:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来很好\N{\rEng}Man, it sounds great,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.78,0:34:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们现在没多少钱\N{\rEng}but we don't have a lot of money right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.96,0:34:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的教会有时会资助需要帮助的失聪人士\N{\rEng}Well, sometimes our church sponsors deaf people in need,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.08,0:34:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而现在\N{\rEng}and right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.07,0:34:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你符合条件  鲁本\N{\rEng}you fit the bill, Ruben.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.05,0:34:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们真的不是那种\N{\rEng}We're really not
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.06,0:34:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-会去教堂的人  -抱歉  我得读...\N{\rEng}- churchgoing people. - Sorry, I-I read...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.47,0:34:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  鲁本  我得读唇语  我没...\N{\rEng}Sorry, Ruben, I read lips. I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.02,0:34:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才说什么\N{\rEng}What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.48,0:34:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们两个都不信教\N{\rEng}We're not religious, either of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.11,0:34:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,对宗教完全不感兴趣\N{\rEng}Very much not into religion.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.58,0:34:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,无意冒犯\N{\rEng}No offense, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.24,0:34:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,宗教与此无关  鲁本\N{\rEng}Religion plays no part in this, Ruben.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.43,0:34:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,教会帮助\N{\rEng}The church helps
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.71,0:34:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,有需要的人  而不是信教的人\N{\rEng}people in need, not religious people.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.98,0:34:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,重要的是你想留在这里\N{\rEng}The important thing is that you want to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.70,0:34:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.68,0:34:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,露\N{\rEng}Lou?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.95,0:34:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得鲁本现在需要帮助吗\N{\rEng}Do you think Ruben needs help right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.43,0:34:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你要明白如果...\N{\rEng}You understand, if, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.77,0:34:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁本打算留在这里\N{\rEng}Ruben were to stay here,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.30,0:34:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他就得靠自己了\N{\rEng}he'd have to do it on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.92,0:34:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都住在与外界隔绝的房子里\N{\rEng}Members live in a house separate from the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.63,0:34:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,与外界没有联系\N{\rEng}No contact to the outside world,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.18,0:34:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,没有电话\N{\rEng}no phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.38,0:34:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我发现无论怎样  这都是最好的办法\N{\rEng}I've found that in all cases, that's the way it works best.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.51,0:34:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,慢一点  好吗\N{\rEng}Yo, hold up a minute, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.17,0:35:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看完  好吗\N{\rEng}Let me catch up. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.52,0:35:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你能帮鲁本下这个决心吗  露\N{\rEng}Can you help Ruben commit to that, Lou?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.05,0:35:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你想...你想先试几天吗\N{\rEng}You want... you want to try this for a couple days?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.63,0:35:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有自己的家\N{\rEng}We have our own home.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.93,0:35:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以住在房车里\N{\rEng}We can stay in the RV.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.84,0:35:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不  很遗憾  我们这里\N{\rEng}No, I'm sorry to say, that's not the way
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.38,0:35:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不允许这样  鲁本\N{\rEng}that it works here, Ruben.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.47,0:35:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那就有问题了\N{\rEng}Well, that's a problem, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.98,0:35:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这段时间里你有地方可去吗  露\N{\rEng}Do you have anywhere you can be during this time, Lou?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.24,0:35:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样吧  不说了\N{\rEng}Yo, that's that, man. We're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.59,0:35:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不说了\N{\rEng}We're done.
