Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.92,1:14:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  很简单的\N{\rEng}Wait, yo, it's easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.29,1:14:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,很简单的  只要慢慢来\N{\rEng}It's easy. Just... slowly.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.12,1:14:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这是为了她\N{\rEng}It's for her, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.42,1:14:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这是为了她\N{\rEng}It's for her.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.28,1:14:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要钱  我们需要钱\N{\rEng}We need money. We need money.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.15,1:14:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这是为了我们\N{\rEng}It's for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.14,1:15:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你说实话\N{\rEng}I'm leveling with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.56,1:15:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这是为了她\N{\rEng}It's for her.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.76,1:15:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这些\N{\rEng}For-for this?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.18,1:15:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这些  记住\N{\rEng}For this, remember it's, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.05,1:15:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,收现金\N{\rEng}it's, uh... cash.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.49,1:15:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗  不收支票\N{\rEng}Okay? Not check.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.01,1:15:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Cool.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.08,1:15:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你没问题吧\N{\rEng}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.66,1:15:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,确定吗\N{\rEng}Sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.99,1:16:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord0\shad1}听觉矫正
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.33,1:16:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord0\shad1}我们的听觉矫治专家\N朱丽叶·卢阿斯
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.46,1:17:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是普林斯听觉矫治吗\N{\rEng}Hi. Is that Prince Audiology?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.63,1:17:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你能听见我说话吗\N{\rEng}Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.65,1:17:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord0\shad1}下午好  有什么能帮助您的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.54,1:17:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord0\shad1}能听见  请告诉我您的姓名
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.77,1:17:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫斯通  鲁本·斯通\N{\rEng}It's Stone, Ruben Stone.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.16,1:17:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁莽的鲁  本来的本\N{\rEng}R-u-b-e-n,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.64,1:17:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,斯通  斯文的斯  通常的通\N{\rEng}Stone, S-T-O-N-E.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.94,1:17:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我要确认预约\N{\rEng}I'm confirming an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.18,1:17:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord0\shad1}好的  斯通先生  请您...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.99,1:17:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我可以等\N{\rEng}Yeah, I can hold.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.55,1:18:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说\N{\rEng}So, listen.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.64,1:18:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-你说什么  写下来  -好\N{\rEng}- What did you say? Write it down. - Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.15,1:18:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我听不见你说话  写下来\N{\rEng}I can't hear you. Write it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.12,1:19:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个提议\N{\rEng}I got a proposition for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.42,1:19:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,什么提议\N{\rEng}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.12,1:19:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我就这个价卖给你\N{\rEng}What if I give it to you at this price...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.46,1:19:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但附加一个条件如何\N{\rEng}but on one condition?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.45,1:19:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以选择在八周内再次联系你\N{\rEng}I have the option of coming back to you within eight weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.34,1:19:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,行吗  从你手上赎回来\N{\rEng}Okay? I get to buy it back off you
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.80,1:19:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,再多给你10%的利息\N{\rEng}for ten percent more than this.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.04,1:19:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但一切都得维持原状\N{\rEng}But everything has to be in its current condition.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.84,1:19:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,现在什么样到时候就要什么样\N{\rEng}Everything has to be exactly like it is now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.92,1:19:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得可以吗\N{\rEng}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.38,1:19:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你何必这么做呢\N{\rEng}Why would you want to do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.22,1:19:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,老兄  我听不见你说话  我聋了\N{\rEng}Dude, I can't hear you. I'm deaf.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.69,1:19:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,要么接受  要么拉倒\N{\rEng}So it's... take it or leave it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.78,1:19:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么决定\N{\rEng}What's it gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.40,1:20:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord0\shad1}乔\N我没事\N我明天就回来\N不用担心\N鲁本
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.91,1:21:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord0\shad1}手术很顺利  鲁本\N我们绕过了你的耳道\N所以这段时间你完全听不到声音
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.12,1:21:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord0\shad1}四周后你要回来激活设备
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.93,1:22:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你回来了\N{\rEng}You're back?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.60,1:22:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,坐吧\N{\rEng}Have a seat here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.25,1:22:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.24,1:22:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了\N{\rEng}I did the deed.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.43,1:22:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,做了什么\N{\rEng}The deed?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.40,1:22:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,手术\N{\rEng}Surgery.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.09,1:22:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你从哪弄来的钱\N{\rEng}How'd you get the money?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.43,1:22:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我卖了房车和其它有的没的\N{\rEng}I sold my RV and other shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.01,1:23:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-好吧  -听我说  乔\N{\rEng}- Okay. - Look, Joe,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.01,1:23:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在真的不想做太多解释\N{\rEng}I really don't want to explain myself right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.54,1:23:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗\N{\rEng}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.11,1:23:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候了  好吗\N{\rEng}It's time. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.81,1:23:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候了  我得做点什么\N{\rEng}It's time. I got to do something.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.97,1:23:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\rEng}Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.21,1:23:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我在拯救我的人生\N{\rEng}Trying to save my f-fuckin' life.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.59,1:23:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我在做的事\N{\rEng}So, that's what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.88,1:23:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,行吗  因为没人会救我\N{\rEng}Okay? No one else is gonna save my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.77,1:23:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吗\N{\rEng}Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.55,1:23:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我坐在这里无所事事\N{\rEng}If I just sit here and diddle around,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.08,1:23:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我能得到什么  我会一无所有\N{\rEng}what am I gonna have? Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.30,1:23:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\rEng}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.29,1:23:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这一切\N{\rEng}And all this shit?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.16,1:23:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,重要吗  有什么意义\N{\rEng}Like, what does it matter? What does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.58,1:23:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,反正都会过去的\N{\rEng}It just passes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.06,1:23:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我消失了\N{\rEng}If I disappear,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.80,1:23:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,有谁会在意\N{\rEng}like, who cares?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.83,1:23:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,没人会在意\N{\rEng}Nobody cares, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.24,1:23:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,真的\N{\rEng}Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.15,1:23:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但没关系\N{\rEng}Yo, and that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.38,1:23:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是人生\N{\rEng}That's life.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.24,1:23:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是人生\N{\rEng}That's life.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.19,1:23:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我是认真的  好吗\N{\rEng}No, for real. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.19,1:23:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,都会过去的\N{\rEng}It just passes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.25,1:23:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的说过去就过去了\N{\rEng}It just fucking... fucking passes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.26,1:23:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想\N{\rEng}I wonder, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.68,1:24:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你在我的书房待了那么多个上午\N{\rEng}all these mornings you've been sitting in my study,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.88,1:24:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,坐在那里\N{\rEng}sitting,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.14,1:24:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有\N{\rEng}have you...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.98,1:24:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,感受到过\N{\rEng}had any...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.20,1:24:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,片刻的\N{\rEng}moments of...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.81,1:24:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,平静呢\N{\rEng}stillness?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.29,1:24:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你说得对  鲁本\N{\rEng}Because you're right, Ruben.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.48,1:24:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,世界在不断前进\N{\rEng}The world does keep moving,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.59,1:24:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,同时它也是个\N{\rEng}and it can be a damn...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.69,1:24:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,很残酷的地方\N{\rEng}cruel place.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.58,1:24:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但对我而言\N{\rEng}But for me...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.61,1:24:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那些平静的时刻\N{\rEng}those moments of stillness,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.24,1:24:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那个地方\N{\rEng}that place, that's the...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.48,1:24:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就是天国\N{\rEng}kingdom of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.28,1:24:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那个地方\N{\rEng}And that place
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.78,1:24:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,永远都不会抛弃你\N{\rEng}will never abandon you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.80,1:24:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但是\N{\rEng}But...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.68,1:24:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到你已经做出了选择\N{\rEng}I see you've made your choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.97,1:24:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\rEng}Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.50,1:24:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.01,1:25:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我也衷心希望\N{\rEng}And I sincerely hope
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.75,1:25:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你的选择能带给你幸福  鲁本\N{\rEng}that it brings you happiness, Ruben.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.26,1:25:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.60,1:25:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想  乔  不知道能不能...\N{\rEng}I was wondering, Joe. I don't know if it's possible...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.33,1:25:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要钱\N{\rEng}but, uh, I need money
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.91,1:25:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,赎回我的房车\N{\rEng}to... just to buy back my RV.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.12,1:25:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样\N{\rEng}You know?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.44,1:25:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我和露\N{\rEng}You know, me... me and Lou.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.16,1:25:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我们的住所\N{\rEng}This is where we live.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.96,1:25:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们的家  我们的家\N{\rEng}It's our home. Our home.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.43,1:25:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝对会还钱给你\N{\rEng}And I can... I can totally pay you back.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.83,1:25:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,只是\N{\rEng}Just, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.18,1:25:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,现在时间紧迫\N{\rEng}Now I got an issue with time.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.79,1:25:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁本\N{\rEng}Ruben.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.52,1:25:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你让自己陷入了何种境地\N{\rEng}I don't understand the situation that you've put yourself in,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.27,1:26:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但是\N{\rEng}but...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.75,1:26:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,在我看来\N{\rEng}from where I'm sitting...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.81,1:26:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在的行为举止像是毒瘾犯了\N{\rEng}you look and sound like an addict.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.44,1:26:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不是  我没有\N{\rEng}No, I don't. Yo, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.68,1:26:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有\N{\rEng}I'm not... It's not...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.47,1:26:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,犯毒瘾\N{\rEng}Not an addi...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.68,1:26:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事\N{\rEng}It's fine. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.71,1:26:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我的情况很好  好吗\N{\rEng}My situation, it's cool. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.29,1:26:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真的  我女友她爸很有钱\N{\rEng}Seriously, my girlfriend's dad is rich,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.97,1:26:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他可以给我钱\N{\rEng}he can give me... give me the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.66,1:26:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这没什么的\N{\rEng}Okay? This is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.99,1:26:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,根本就不是事儿\N{\rEng}You can't imagine how nothing this is.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.75,1:26:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真的\N{\rEng}Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.70,1:26:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我太蠢了  很抱歉我问你借钱\N{\rEng}I'm fucking stupid. I'm-I'm sorry to ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.26,1:26:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  好吗\N{\rEng}I'm sorry. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.48,1:26:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.62,1:26:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  我能在这里\N{\rEng}Please, can I stay here for just...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.43,1:26:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,再住三四周吗\N{\rEng}three, four weeks?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.83,1:26:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,等他们\N{\rEng}Till they...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.80,1:26:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,激活设备\N{\rEng}activate?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.20,1:27:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁本\N{\rEng}Ruben.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.59,1:27:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你也知道  这里的人\N{\rEng}As you know, everybody here
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.33,1:27:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,都坚信\N{\rEng}shares in the belief that
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.07,1:27:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,失聪不是残疾\N{\rEng}being deaf is not a handicap.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.34,1:27:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要修复\N{\rEng}Not something to fix.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.76,1:27:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这一点对这里的人很重要\N{\rEng}It's pretty important around here.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.43,1:27:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这些孩子\N{\rEng}All these kids...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.73,1:27:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们所有人\N{\rEng}all of us,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.71,1:27:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,每天都需要将此\N{\rEng}need to be reminded of it
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.31,1:27:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,铭记在心\N{\rEng}every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.35,1:27:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我的机构以这一信念为根基\N{\rEng}And my house is a house built on that belief,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.32,1:27:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,以信任为根基\N{\rEng}and built on trust.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.63,1:27:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,当那份信任被打破\N{\rEng}And when that trust is violated,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.40,1:27:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,会产生后果\N{\rEng}things happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.73,1:27:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,而我不能容忍\N{\rEng}And I can't have that.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.36,1:27:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有许多其他人\N{\rEng}There are too many others
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.35,1:27:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,需要关照\N{\rEng}to consider.
