Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.21,1:45:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我想许个愿\N{\rEng}I would like to make a wish.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.92,1:45:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望我的女儿和我一起唱一首歌\N{\rEng}I would like my daughter to sing a little song with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.09,1:45:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸  不要\N{\rEng}Papa, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.88,1:45:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我有权许这个愿  今天是我的生日\N{\rEng}This is my right... It's my birthday!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.30,1:45:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\rEng}Come.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.22,1:45:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你们中有些人\N{\rEng}Some of you knew
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.52,1:45:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,认识露易丝的母亲\N{\rEng}Louise's mother,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.90,1:45:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,也知道我曾为她写过歌\N{\rEng}and know that I wrote songs for her.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.85,1:45:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,写过许多首\N{\rEng}Many.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.48,1:45:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这首是你小时候的最爱\N{\rEng}And this was your favorite when you were little.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.11,1:45:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你记得吗\N{\rEng}Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.59,1:47:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 色彩皆褪去 ♪\N{\rEng}♪ S'effacent, les couleurs ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.39,1:47:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 在这房间里 ♪\N{\rEng}♪ Entre quatre murs ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.64,1:47:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 这份爱如此疯狂 ♪\N{\rEng}♪ Cet amour, c'est fou ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.23,1:47:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 你未曾体会 ♪\N{\rEng}♪ Que tu n'as pas connu ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.86,1:47:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 这份爱又一次杀死我 ♪\N{\rEng}♪ Cet amour me tue, encore ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.79,1:47:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 我的爱 ♪\N{\rEng}♪ Mon amour ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.37,1:47:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 我已死去 ♪\N{\rEng}♪ Je meurs ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.74,1:48:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\rEng}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.83,1:48:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好的\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.24,1:49:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\rEng}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.57,1:49:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我得喝点水\N{\rEng}I just need some water.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.83,1:49:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\rEng}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.09,1:49:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,还好吗\N{\rEng}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.21,1:49:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没事  只是有点干燥\N{\rEng}Yeah, it's just a little dry in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.80,1:49:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚的派对\N{\rEng}That was... that was...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.68,1:49:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,挺棒的\N{\rEng}pretty cool tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.39,1:49:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你唱得太好听了\N{\rEng}You sounded fucking great.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.72,1:49:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-得了吧  -怎么了\N{\rEng}- Yeah, right. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.31,1:49:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,别告诉我你唱的时候没动感情\N{\rEng}You're telling me you weren't feeling it?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.27,1:49:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-你当时很投入  -好吧\N{\rEng}- You were in it. - Well, yeah, well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.48,1:49:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,毫无疑问  你那么唱歌好听极了\N{\rEng}Straight up, you sounded amazing singing like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.52,1:49:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我爸写的歌\N{\rEng}It's my dad's stuff, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:40.65,1:49:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在会说法语了\N{\rEng}And you're speaking French now?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.98,1:49:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,老天  只会一点点\N{\rEng}Oh, my God, barely.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.86,1:49:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道你会说法语\N{\rEng}I didn't know you could do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:45.03,1:49:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我都快忘光了  不过\N{\rEng}Well, I've mostly forgotten, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.69,1:49:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,开始慢慢捡起来了\N{\rEng}it's coming back a little.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.24,1:49:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才还在想  你记得吗\N{\rEng}Yeah, I was thinking, like, do you remember...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.16,1:49:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,记得这个地方吗\N{\rEng}you remember this place at all?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.45,1:49:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,之前不记得  但是\N{\rEng}I didn't, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.83,1:49:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己都不知道有些事情\N{\rEng}so disconcerting the things that
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.79,1:50:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,还在记忆中留存  挺让人困惑的\N{\rEng}your memory holds onto without you knowing.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.46,1:50:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道  我...\N{\rEng}I don't know, my...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.34,1:50:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈从没跟我说起过这个地方\N{\rEng}my mom and I never really talked about this place.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.80,1:50:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我脑中只有模糊的奇怪印象  但是\N{\rEng}It was always some weird, dreamy idea, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.43,1:50:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,现在慢慢开始想起来了\N{\rEng}I mean, now it's come back a little.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.35,1:50:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.89,1:50:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.44,1:50:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟大家讲了我们吉普赛人式的生活\N{\rEng}I told everyone about our little gypsy life together.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.86,1:50:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我很怀念\N{\rEng}I miss it.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.27,1:50:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得重回那种生活\N{\rEng}We got to get back into it.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.11,1:50:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要回到那种生活\N{\rEng}You know? We got to get back on it,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.65,1:50:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要找回那种\N{\rEng}we got to get back in the fuckin'...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.28,1:50:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那种状态  对吗\N{\rEng}in the groove, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.99,1:50:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你说呢\N{\rEng}Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.86,1:50:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我得把房车的事搞定\N{\rEng}I got to go get the Airstream sorted.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.20,1:50:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,搞定什么\N{\rEng}What do you mean "sorted"?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.62,1:50:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就是  就是有一大堆事情要做\N{\rEng}I just, I just got a shit ton of things to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.95,1:50:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-是吧  -嗯  是说巡演的事吗\N{\rEng}- You know? - Right. Like, with the tour and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.25,1:50:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-是啊  巡演什么的  -嗯\N{\rEng}- Yeah, the fuckin' tour, everything. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:41.62,1:50:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得重回以前的生活\N{\rEng}Like, we just got to get back on it,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.87,1:50:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都要继续\N{\rEng}you know, everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.63,1:50:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,专辑  巡演\N{\rEng}The album, the tour...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.46,1:50:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,还有...是吧\N{\rEng}the-the... you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.38,1:50:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.75,1:51:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系  露\N{\rEng}It's okay, Lou.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.63,1:51:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.72,1:51:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\rEng}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:40.97,1:51:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,什么没关系\N{\rEng}What's okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.48,1:51:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你拯救了我\N{\rEng}You saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.20,1:51:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我\N{\rEng}You made it...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.70,1:51:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我的人生变得美好\N{\rEng}you made it beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.30,1:52:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,所以没关系\N{\rEng}So it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.83,1:52:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.71,1:52:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么说这些\N{\rEng}Why are you saying this?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:17.64,1:52:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你也拯救了我  鲁比\N{\rEng}You saved my life, too, Rubi.


